    {
      "id": "type-definition-contract-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Type Definition Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -220,
        "y": -160
      },
      "width": 680,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Type Definition Contract\n\nA type definition is the declared identity that should populate the legend and drive host-facing consumers.\n\nIt must name the type, point to the implementing node class, and state the semantic meaning other surfaces should trust."
      }
    },
